## Installation

```bash
# Build the plugin
go build -buildmode=plugin -o {{.PluginName}}.so main.go

# Install the plugin
nixai plugin install ./{{.PluginName}}.so
```

## Usage

```bash
# Execute basic operation
nixai plugin execute {{.PluginName}} basic-operation --input "test data"

# Query plugin information
nixai plugin execute {{.PluginName}} info-query

# Check plugin status
nixai plugin status {{.PluginName}}
```

